<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-11-08T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-11-08T00:00:00-05:00" n="197" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d197">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source"><persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1" type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to Prime Minister <persName corresp="#p_CC2" type="to">Churchill</persName></hi><note n="1" xml:id="d197fn1">Sent to the United States Naval Attaché, London,
                                via Navy channels.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi></seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-11-08">8 November 1943</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Number 412 from the President to the <gloss target="#t_FormerNavalPerson1">Former Naval Person</gloss> secret
                            and personal.</p>
                        <p>Your 493.<note n="2" xml:id="d197fn2">Ante, <ref target="#pg_156">p.
                                    156</ref>.</note></p>
                        <p>I accept your suggestion that “Commanders responsible” in Paragraph 3 be
                            changed to “Combined Chiefs of Staff” and have so informed <persName corresp="#p_HWA2">Harriman</persName> and have authorized him to
                            attach agreement to the protocol.</p>
                        <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_RFD1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>